childish /ˈtʃaɪldɪʃ/

1. ADJ Childish means relating to or typical of a child. 孩子的; 孩子特有的 

例： ...childish enthusiasm. …孩子特有的热情。 

2. ADJ If you describe someone, especially an adult, as childish , you disapprove of them because they behave in an immature way. 幼稚的 [表不满] 

例： ...Penny's selfish and childish behaviour. …佩尼自私而幼稚的行为。

</div>

